title: Cafe Madame Negla
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Italian, Take-out, Brunch, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has some vegan and vegetarian menu items including vegan burgers. Other items include cupcakes, cake, muffins, enchiladas, sandwiches, crepes. Street parking. Interior Japanese style decor.
